      <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
    
         <p>The Lyon Lumber Co. owned timber lands in Linn County, Oregon. It was called Lyon Cypress Lumber Co. until 1916.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <prefercite encodinganalog="524">
    
         <p>Lyon Lumber Company records, Mss 1720, Oregon Historical Society Research Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent encodinganalog="5202_">
    
         <p>Records of the Lyon Lumber Company include correspondence, deeds, abstracts of title, minutes, accounts, stock certificates, ledgers and registers regarding land in Oregon and Louisiana. Materials on microfilm include minute books of director meetings, stockholder meetings and annual reports, 1902-1931.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
